[I] Tiling window manager built on Mir

[T] miracle-wm is a Wayland compositor based on Mir. It features a tiling
[T] window manager at its core, very much in the style of i3 and sway.

[U] https://miracle-wm.org/

[A] miracle-wm Developers
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/wayland
[F] CROSS

[L] GPL
[V] 0.10.0

[D] 3b9324d12a1e6b828249e621b809cfbd69c61f94862b1e5c9d59a452 miracle-wm-0.10.0.tar.gz https://github.com/miracle-wm-org/miracle-wm/archive/v0.10.0/

var_append GCC_WRAPPER_APPEND ' ' "-I$(pkgprefix includedir glib) -L$(pkgprefix libdir glib)"

var_append cmakeopt ' ' -DENABLE_TESTS=OFF
